# surface at runtime.
# BLOCKER: transitive via pinned @opentelemetry/sdk-node ^0.211.0; the vulnerable Prometheus HTTP listener is never started in our config (OTLP-only egress), so the malformed-request DoS is structurally unreachable; revisit when the syncpack OpenTelemetry pin advances past 0.220
